(alter-meta! (resolve 'clojure.core/partial) fill {:arglists (quote ([f] [f arg1] [f arg1 arg2] [f arg1 arg2 arg3] [f arg1 arg2 arg3 & more])), :doc "Takes a function f and fewer than the normal arguments to f, and\n  returns a fn that takes a variable number of additional args. When\n  called, the returned function calls f with args + additional args."})
